hwDetectEngineOAMEnable.description: Globally enable or disable the detect-engine for oam. If the hwDetectEngineOAMEnable is 1, detect-engine for oam is enabled. If the hwDetectEngineOAMEnable is 2, detect-engine for oam is disabled. By default, detect-engine for oam is enabled.
